author: dblevins
msg: Added explicit message to when something a remote interfaces passes/returns/throws is not serializable.

Message explicitly says that remote interfaces are only allowed to pass serializable objects per EJB specification and shows how to disable that behavior.  The hope is to avoid anyone thinking that this some sort of failure on OpenEJB's part.
